I found this problem regular.

first, my program topogoly like list:
lbs-springmvc  ->  lbs-motan-rpc

When program started, before motan-rpc bean worked, access it, then of course exception. And now go to web to look over topogoly view, its none.

When I look over the response of uri /api/topogoly, found the json that is invalid according to the prompt "Cannot return null for non-nullable type: 'String' within parent 'Call' (/getClusterTopology/calls[0]/callType)".

if callType that in the response of uri /api/topogoly is empty, the problem will happen, like this:
```
{
	"data": {
		"getClusterTopology": {
			"nodes": [{
				"id": "-1",
				"name": "Your_ApplicationName",
				"type": "SpringMVC",
				"sla": 100,
				"cpm": 0,
				"avgResponseTime": 4,
				"apdex": 100,
				"isAlarm": false,
				"numOfServer": 5,
				"numOfServerAlarm": 0,
				"numOfServiceAlarm": 0
			}, {
				"id": "1",
				"name": "User",
				"type": "USER"
			}],
			"calls": [{
				"source": "-1",
				"target": "-1",
				"isAlert": false,
				"callType": "Motan",
				"cpm": 0,
				"avgResponseTime": 4
			}, {
				"source": "1",
